  "content": "Meet Irakli, a recent university graduate who works as a Software Engineer for Google Health in London. His team works on Fitbit\u2019s Personal Health Assistant, a Gemini-powered AI coach designed to create deeply customized fitness, sleep and nutrition plans for users worldwide.\n\nFor him, finding your niche is all about having the flexibility to explore different spaces early on. \u201cThe best thing here is the opportunity to work on different things, which is really nice for helping you find yourself at the start of your career,\u201d he explains.\n\nWant to build AI that impacts everyday well-being like Irakli does? Explore our open student and early career roles \u2192 https://goo.gle/4vOpWSf",
