  "linkedinUrl": "https://www.linkedin.com/posts/google_meet-wei-a-forward-deployed-engineer-fde-activity-7480375037418565632-5vVV",
  "content": "Meet Wei, a Forward Deployed Engineer (FDE) at Google Singapore. Wei built his career in AI by teaching himself machine learning with open-source tools. Today, he uses that proactive curiosity to bring advanced cloud technology directly to global businesses \u2014 like a recent project co-building safety guardrails for a bank\u2019s generative AI financial products. \n\nBy collaborating with internal Product and Engineering teams, Wei turns customer feedback into upgraded product features. He credits his supportive Singapore office community with keeping his well-being balanced and confidence high. \"I might not know everything, but knowing there is always someone around who can help gives me the confidence to tackle new technical challenges,\u201d he says. And to stay ahead in a fast-moving field, he shares that continuous learning is non-negotiable. \n\nWant to build cutting-edge AI tools with a team that always has your back? Join our collaborative community in Singapore and explore open Forward Deployed Engineering positions today \u2192 https://goo.gle/3PUwMWc",
